David Neil CARR, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
STATE of Florida, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-4800 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. January 11, 2019

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed for failure of the appellant to comply with this court's December 6, 2018, order requesting the submission of an amended notice of appeal that identifies the date of the order for which review is sought.

LaROSE, C.J., and NORTHCUTT and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
